g.text: + args: list of arguments used by the models
+ add_model(model): adds a model to the BM
+ add_arg(arg): adds an argument to the BM
+ sort_values(): sorts the df by values
+ sort_models(): sorts the df by model names
+ sort_args(): sorts the df by arguments names
+ sort(): sorts the df by both args and models
+ load_df(): loads the df from its path
+ save_df(): saves the df at its path
+ populate(): call on compute if no df is found
+ compute_df(): calls models eval function for each argument
+ plot_df(): show and saves the image from the df
Model (this one is not coded, too general)
+ eval(arg): returns the score of the model when evaluating the arg

g.text: + model_name: name of the model used
+ open_dirs(snr, path): opens the right dirs
+ compute_noisy_dir(snr, path): adds noise to all files
+ denoise_dir(snr, path): denoise all files in the right snr dir
+ compare_dirs(snr, path): calculate snr by comparing a dir
+ eval(snr, path="./dataset"): wrap all of the above and returns snr
+ textPath: path of the true texts
+ model_path: path to the model used by the STT (most likely a path)
+ estimateText(wavFilePath): uses model to estimate text from wavFile
+ ComputeWERfromDir(directory, out_dir): estimate texts from directory
+ eval(directory): wrap all of the above and returns wer
